trans-unit.source: Provides static methods and properties for <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.BooleanObject" /> 对象的静态方法和属性。

trans-unit.source: All methods of this class are called by passing in a reference to the object that is requesting access to the method.
